            "title": "Tailoring work participation support for cancer survivors using the stages of change: perspectives of (health care) professionals and survivors",
            "description": "Interventions to support work participation in cancer survivors (CSs) have shown limited effectiveness. Applying a behavioral change framework (stages of change) could make work participation interventions for CSs more timely and tailored. We explored the application of the stages of change framework to work participation support for CSs and generated stage-specific intervention content to be tested in our randomized controlled trial.",
